This Job principaly launch the hping command for monitoring TCP RTT. It sends syslog in case of error.

Required Arguments:
  - dest : it is the IP destination you want to ping

Optionnal Arguments:
  all the arguments of the ping command are accepted

Statistics: it doesn't produce any statistic

Example:
  - Ping 172.20.0.83 : -a "destination_ip 172.20.0.83"
  - Ping 172.20.0.83 with packets of size 100 bytes : -a "destination_ip 172.20.0.83" "packetsize 100"

